Rating: 4
Really nice. I followed the reviewer suggestion to mix the salt with the zucchini and let it sit for a while first (I did it for at least an hour), to get out the excess water content. This worked well. I also made up the dressing in a jar to pass at the table- it's too much dressing for the salad. Also, if they are stored separately, the dressing won't cause the salad to wilt in the fridge. Delicious and refreshing!

